title: EYL #201 Eric Thomas on Motivation & Building a Multi-Million Dollar Empire
itunes:title: EYL #201 Eric Thomas on Motivation & Building a Multi-Million Dollar Empire
description:
Eric Thomas on Motivation & Building a Multi-Million Dollar Empire

In episode 201 we spoke with the legendary Eric Thomas and his brilliant business partner Carlas Quinney Jr. aka CJ. They broke down their business relationship and explained the inner workings on how they have been able to build a multi million dollar brand. 

They also spoke about the business of public speaking, writing a book, and teamwork. #ericthomas #motivation #motivationalspeaker
